{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe185c38d5","title":"首都大专院校红卫兵革命造反总司令部第二号通令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"52fa3c2bdf","index":0,"year":1966,"month":10,"day":9,"articleId":"fe185c38d5","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"资产阶级反动路线","id":"70f02a0dc7","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0e7f404b71","type":"title","text":"首都大专院校红卫兵革命造反总司令部第二号通令","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"525e7aa427","type":"paragraph","text":"首都大专院校红卫兵革命造反总司令部第二号通令","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"632a2b2129","type":"paragraph","text":"首都大专院校红卫兵革命造反总司令部","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d45879a077","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.10.09","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bf42dbc2e8","type":"paragraph","text":"党中央认为，在无产阶级文化大革命中，犯过方向错误、路线错误的同志，应当正视自己的错误，改正自己的错误，回到正确立场、正确路线上来，而不要发展到同党对抗的地步。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94f7ac4dc7","type":"paragraph","text":"──摘自《红旗》一九六六年十三期社论","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"476cdb911b","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中央军委和总政治部的紧急指示，及屡次中央首长讲话的精神，我们特此发出紧急通令：","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"50b5957488","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 各单位文革领导人应当马上行动起来，采取有效措施，不折不扣的执行党中央、中央军委和总政治部的指示。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1fc2fb974","type":"paragraph","text":"二、 各单位立即召开大会，对在运动初期被工作组扣上反党帽子，黑帮帽子，“假左派”、“真右派”的革命群众进行平反。当众恢复名誉，并把非法整理的材料，全部退回本人。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40a4ea2ba1","type":"paragraph","text":"三、 工作组负责人应当是随叫随到，随时准备听取群众的批判。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f47a9b10b","type":"paragraph","text":"四、 不许某些别有用心的人打着‘串连’的旗号，企图逃避本单位两条路线斗争。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d9cc77dca","type":"paragraph","text":"我们深信大多数有问题的当权派和工作组负责人是要革命的，是可以改正错误的！但是，如果有人坚持反动路线，则不管他是谁，职位有多高，“声望”有多大，我们都要和他拼个死活，把他打倒在地，踏上一只脚，使他永世不得翻身。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40d7bc59ba","type":"paragraph","text":"踢开一切绊脚石，扫除一切害人虫，全无敌！","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"027f974416","type":"paragraph","text":"载《首都红卫兵》第五号","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ae8f4f4f4","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年十月九日）","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe185c38d5","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}